## Kom igång

Ladda ner repot.

---

## Installera packages

dotnet add package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore
dotnet new xunit -n CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests
dotnet add CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests reference CurrencyDeltaApi.csproj

---

## Bygg och kör

dotnet clean
dotnet build
dotnet run

---

## Testa med Postman

Starta applikationen:
dotnet run

Gör en POST request till:
[https://localhost:xxxx/currencydelta](https://localhost:xxxx/currencydelta)

Sätt header:
Content-Type: application/json

Body:
{
"baseline": "GBP",
"currencies": ["USD"],
"fromDate": "2025-01-01",
"toDate": "2025-01-10"
}

---

## Kör tester

dotnet test CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests
